# Liabilities Provisions Restructuring Costs Amount

## identifier
de1470

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, for all provisions raised for the restructuring of an organisation.

## guidance
This includes severance, termination and redundancy payments and integration costs.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Provisions.RestructuringCosts.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.00
- period=instant
